317168928.Title: Samsung BESPOKE 4-Door Flex French Door Smart Refrigerator with Beverage Center and Customizable Panels
317168928.Description: Samsung's Smart Counter Depth 4-Door Flex refrigerator with customizable door panels available in eight colors and two finishes. It features a Beverage Center with both a water dispenser and AutoFill Water Pitcher. It includes a a Dual Ice Maker with Ice Bites, smaller nugget ice.
